  <brief_title>Using Ultrasound to Predict Response to Intraarticular Corticosteroids in Knee Osteoarthritis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Using Ultrasound to Predict Response to Intraarticular Corticosteroids in Knee Osteoarthritis: A Randomized Placebo-Controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
